<body class="h-full">
    <div id="root" class="h-full">
        <div class="container py-5">
            <div class="text-center mb-5">
                <img src="/assets/img/technico.png" alt="Technico Logo" class="img-fluid mb-4" style="max-width: 200px;">
                <h1 class="display-4">Welcome to Technico</h1>
                <p class="lead">
                    Our team at Technico is here to provide expert services tailored to your needs across Greece.
                    Whether you're looking for professional painting, reliable insulation solutions, precise frame installation, efficient plumbing, or safe and effective electrical work,
                    we've got you covered. With skilled and trusted professionals, we ensure every job is completed with quality and care.
                    Big or small, your project is in good hands with Technico!
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-md-2 row-cols-lg-3 g-4">
                <div class="col">
                    <div class="card shadow-sm">
                        <img src="/assets/img/painting.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="Painting services">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title">Painting</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">
                                From a fresh coat to a complete color overhaul, our painting experts deliver high-quality results with attention
                                to detail and a commitment to excellence. Whether it’s reviving walls, ceilings, or woodwork, we use premium paints
                                and professional techniques to enhance the look and longevity of every surface.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col">
                    <div class="card shadow-sm">
                        <img src="/assets/img/insulation.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="Insulation services">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title">Insulation</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">
                                Whether it’s insulating walls, sealing floors, or protecting your roof, our insulation specialists will ensure a high-quality
                                finish that boosts energy efficiency and comfort in your space. Trust us to keep your property powered safely and reliably.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col">
                    <div class="card shadow-sm">
                        <img src="/assets/img/frame.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="Frame services">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title">Frame</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">
                                Our framing experts provide solid structural solutions that form the backbone of any construction project.
                                From load-bearing walls to custom partitions, we ensure safety and durability for years to come.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col">
                    <div class="card shadow-sm">
                        <img src="/assets/img/plumbing.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="Plumbing services">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title">Plumbing</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">
                                Our skilled plumbing team offers comprehensive solutions for all your water and drainage needs. From fixing leaks
                                and installing new pipes to managing complex drainage systems, we ensure that your plumbing system is efficient and built to last.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col">
                    <div class="card shadow-sm">
                        <img src="/assets/img/electrics.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="Electrical Work services">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title">Electrical Work</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">
                                Our certified electricians provide a full range of electrical services, from installing new wiring and outlets
                                to upgrading panels. We focus on safety, efficiency, and quality workmanship to meet your electrical needs.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="bg-dark text-white text-center py-3">
